    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Social security arrangements between the UK and the EU from 1 January 2021: staff guide
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This staff guidance explains the social security coordination arrangements between the UK and the EU under the EU Withdrawal Agreement from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
